author: hustla187
title: Kobe Bryant: A Legend in L.A.
review: After Magic and Jabbar, there was no one who could replace them or try to be good as they were. When Kobe was drafted, it was an amazing team. A player that scores 81 points in one game deserves to be a minifigure. Kobe Bryant is a legend already, and is awesome as a minifigure.
